{"tid":1675443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"輸出革命 不如試下開新移民戰線","createTime":"2019-10-26T01:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T11:54:28.000Z","uid":272805,"like":61,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"47f73dda84933b399fc630f0b6e3d57852d667a2","tid":1675443,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:29:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BzMMfxZ-P2g&amp;feature=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR18zJeI14Sflrb5km_7hFSAv9XCg96vQDcGihWkXrjP07c1vxkietLURoE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBzMMfxZ-P2g%26feature%3Dshare%26fbclid%3DIwAR18zJeI14Sflrb5km_7hFSAv9XCg96vQDcGihWkXrjP07c1vxkietLURoE&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtNxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=9944b33b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BzMMfxZ-P2g&amp;feature=share&amp;fbclid=IwAR18zJeI14Sflrb5km_7hFSAv9XCg96vQDcGihWkXrjP07c1vxkietLURoE</a><br />\n<br />\n大家都知每日150目的係想溝淡香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地改變唔到個政策，但可以改變佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n增加150個敵人，不如增加150個自己友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實大陸人係上面往得好過香港，消費又平<br />\n都肯落嚟，咁即係話<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港一定有比大陸優勝的地方</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要做既就係<br />\n1.搵到佢哋肯落嚟嘅原因<br />\n（錢，制度，食物安全之類）<br />\n2.強調呢幾方面比大陸侵蝕緊<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果唔改變，好快就會變成大陸一樣</span></span></strong><br />\n4.搵埋佢地幫手<br />\n<br />\n成功的話，甚至乎有機會改變返個政策<br />\n（政府都唔想每日多150個敵人）<br />\n<br />\nGoogle下專做新來港的ngo係邊度<br />\n就知道係邊度做宣傳最好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hjwu6Lh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhjwu6Lh.png&h=22e9be09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nP牌推唔到，覺得可以既就推一推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3bc731e9189d8eacee6de775e070d6fc771f026e","tid":1675443,"uid":47422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:30:54.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"ab9134e9a1bd835b0f7b7f018321a85c1fef605e","tid":1675443,"uid":272805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:31:24.000Z","msg":"自推 1/5"},{"pid":"7cec7cf073a6eca67b52d8aa035ce632be182748","tid":1675443,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:32:16.000Z","msg":"自推2/5"},{"pid":"6938aed40a101bd4ee235c888ac44d316d2cdbbc","tid":1675443,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:33:37.000Z","msg":"自推3/5"},{"pid":"050d0ce6dab927208180557887efc3d35f4f9637","tid":1675443,"uid":1876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8205b58f29aed61be9c297ab12c41f71c2169b34","tid":1675443,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:35:08.000Z","msg":"自推4/5<br />\n唔好只比正評<br />\n要推呀 手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e755bcabb35db33fde0fd9c7b34b3abe5880ff17","tid":1675443,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:35:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8e6f0439d2c43bc308c3a273801d8858d299ec1f","tid":1675443,"uid":167619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:35:16.000Z","msg":"Gd idea!"},{"pid":"096cc49c80ffcfcb21e841f1ddd25ce9f7d49528","tid":1675443,"uid":167619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:35:38.000Z","msg":"但點實行"},{"pid":"3649fd1b71debc1079803abcf90a0ce17d00d83e","tid":1675443,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T01:35:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><